==Demographics==
As of the census<ref name=census/> of 2020, there were 34 people living in the CDP (down from 39 in 2010). There were 23 housing units. The [[Race and ethnicity in the United States Census|racial makeup]] of the town was 85.3% White, and 5.9% from two or more races. Hispanic or Latino of any race were 0.3% of the population.

